<subSubSection id="4B104AD47FD910B3052F9F10192DF124" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" type="distribution">
<paragraph id="0C5787E557FD489B5A88CF4CF4738DF8" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Distribution.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="48C2CC87E2868F97BCC388F0836E2512" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">
Only known from the Department of 
<normalizedToken id="E42E66DBE71221683565B48C91272BDA" originalValue="Caaguazú">Caaguazu</normalizedToken>
in Paraguay, where it grows in cerrado.
</paragraph>
